==English==
{{wp|Ye (surname)}}
===Etymology 1===
Romanization of the {{der|en|zh|-}} surname {{m|zh|葉|tr=Yè}}.
====Proper noun====
{{en-proper noun|s}}
# {{surname|en|from=Chinese}}.
=====Statistics=====
* According to the 2010 United States Census, ''Ye'' is the 3609<sup>th</sup> most common surname in the United States, belonging to 9839 individuals. ''Ye'' is most common among Asian/Pacific Islander (97.02%) individuals.
